python-ctp
==========

Python wrapper for CTP

Install
-------

::

    pip install ctp_deps
    pip install python-ctp (not open-sourced yet)

Testing
-------

::

    cp conf/simnow.yml.example conf/simnow.yml
    vim conf/simnow.yml # and fill up simnow account
    python setup.py test
